Source: mptcp-bpf-rr
Section: net
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Yannick Chabanois <contact@openmptcprouter.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), clang, libbpf-dev
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: mptcp-bpf-rr
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, libbpf0 | libbpf1
Description: MPTCP BPF RoundRobin Scheduler
 BPF implementation of the MPTCP round-robin scheduler.
 This scheduler distributes data across available subflows
 in a round-robin fashion.
 .
 The compiled BPF object is installed into /usr/share/bpf/scheduler/
 and can be loaded with mptcpd or iproute2.
